c observations and we\nconclude that the framework presented in this work can significantly improve\nthe knowledge of the IGM thermal state, which will in turn guarantee better\nconstraints on IGM-derived cosmological parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Sep 2014 20:00:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Dec 2014 10:27:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-15"}
