usal\nconnection between the presence of the hot flow and the compact jet. We find\nthat the non-thermal component is hardening during the hard state at the\ndecaying stage of the outburst, which indicates that the acceleration\nefficiency is a steep function of radius at low accretion rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Sep 2014 12:22:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 19 Oct 2014 12:35:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-18"}
